reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy, attractive bookcase
reviews.reviewText: We ordered one bookcase and were so pleased with it we ordered two more. We live in a condo with limited storage. These bookcases are attractive, very sturdy, easy to assemble and reasonably priced. We are pleased with the purchase and highly recommend them.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 18, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good enough that I bought a second...
reviews.reviewText: Good quality materials—no flimsy veneers or cheap-feeling particle wood. The finish on the metal supports is even and pleasant to the eye. All of the assembly instructions were clear, the parts clearly labeled, and nothing came damaged or missing. Between my husband and I, we were able to assemble it in about 20 minutes (not counting the time spent trying to find a good wall stud so we could screw in the safety ties).Cupboard space in our kitchen is limited, so I bought this shelf to catch some "overhang" from our regular pantry. It happily holds light stuff (cereal, tea, literal marshmallows...) and heavy stuff (boxes of soda, jarred pasta/grains, bottles of vinegar and olive oil...); everything else we use more frequently than our canned goods and non-perishables. I bought this shelf specifically to match two shorter book shelves that we have in the house, and I even picked up a second to put in our living room (for books, dog treats, and boxes and boxes of puzzles and board games).I expect to be able to move these shelves (and their shorter companions) to my home office when we inevitably move house again. I'll definitely be putting the weight limit to the test by then...

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great aesthetic, sturdy, and great customer service!
reviews.reviewText: Bookshelf is very easy to assemble, probably took about 20 minutes. It looks great and has adjustable knobs on the bottom that make it easy to level. When assembling, I noticed one of my support bars had a stripped thread on the inside, but I emailed customer support and they responded within a few hours. My replacement part made it to me in just a few days. Highly recommend!
